name: Newborn Cocoon
description:
This adorable cocoon is a perfect photo prop for newborn babies. The open stitch will allow for tiny fingers and toes to poke through the cocoon! This cocoon will hold an infant up to about 10 pounds.Can also be used to snuggles your sweet baby to keep him/her warm and toasty. can be done in any colors.
Can get a matching hat for $5
